query:
UPDATE crawl_urls SET
                status = ?1,
                fetched_at = ?2,
                retry_count = ?3,
                last_error = ?4,
                next_retry_at = ?5,
                etag = ?6,
                last_modified = ?7,
                content_hash = ?8,
                document_id = ?9
            WHERE source_id = ?10 AND url = ?11
